summary: Help me give a delayed 🤦🏻‍♀️ Welcome to one of my newest Wellness Coaches!  Rebecca is amazing!  She is 57 years young and has...
caption:
Help me give a delayed 🤦🏻‍♀️ Welcome to one of my newest Wellness Coaches! Rebecca is amazing! She is 57 years young and has been changing her healthy eating habits and getting stronger everyday! She’s also helping her friends and clients do so too!

Together we are better! Time to join us and get jump started on your Wellness goals or to destress from the holidays!

My name is Rebecca I’m a wife a mom and a grandmother. I’m 57 years old my husband and I are retired and live in the country. Ive decided to make a change in my life, i would like the support of my family and friends in my new journey. First I like to say I would never be here if it weren’t for Jennifer Bell Smith. She is the person who started me in this life changing lifestyle. She guided me though and made me believe in myself, that I could do this, I’m greatful for all her help. I fell off the wagon one year ago and returned to my old ways. I’m afraid that I wont be able to do this, but I now have a new coach, Bev Gallant and she’s awesome too. Six years ago I was weighing 190 lbs I never even relized it, how unhealthy and over weight I was until I seen my before and after photos. #coach #wellness #health #fitfam #fitspo #ceo #entrepreneur #motivation #fitspiration #teambeachbody #beach #beachbodycoach
